00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 9=

4
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:09,680
Impudent!

5
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,200
How dare you curse me?

6
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:13,439
Guards, take this person of ill omen...

7
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:13,920
Guards,

8
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:16,879
send Shen Zhinian to the Cold Palace.

9
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:20,719
Your Majesty,

10
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:22,920
are you trying to protect her?

11
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:25,280
I am venting your frustrations,
Dowager Consort.

12
00:01:27,799 --> 00:01:29,640
Liu Ruyan behaved
improperly before the throne.

13
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,750
She will be demoted to Senior Attendant
and confined for one month.

14
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,560
Enough.

15
00:01:36,900 --> 00:01:39,540
(Cold Palace)

16
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:47,120
Young Lady,

17
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:49,560
how can anyone live
in this broken place?

18
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,000
It's fine.

19
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,799
Tinglan Palace wasn't
much bigger than this.

20
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:55,599
We'll clean it up in a bit.

21
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,439
The more others try
to make us miserable,

22
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,159
the more we should live happily.

23
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:01,200
Only you would be so broad-minded,
Young Lady.

24
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:03,920
His Majesty treated you like this,
yet you can still laugh?

25
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,560
If I hadn't entered the Cold Palace,

26
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:07,920
I would have lost my life long ago.

27
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:11,319
We actually have to thank His Majesty.

28
00:02:11,919 --> 00:02:14,520
But being sent to
the Cold Palace is so heartless.

29
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:16,960
His Majesty is
a suspicious man by nature.

30
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,879
I deliberately
approached him in the palace,

31
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,960
and my sister deliberately approached
the Dowager Consort at Mount Nanhua.

32
00:02:22,479 --> 00:02:24,560
How could he not suspect the two of us?

33
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:27,240
But if His Majesty remains suspicious,

34
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,439
will we never be able to get out?

35
00:02:29,439 --> 00:02:31,120
We've been through much worse than this.

36
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,800
We'll deal with whatever

37
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,360
comes our way.

38
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:43,060
(Cold Palace)

39
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:02,039
You scoundrel.

40
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,080
Get out.

41
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,800
What?

42
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,400
You scoundrel.

43
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,360
Get out.

44
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,039
Shen Zhinian,

45
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,919
how dare you hit me...

46
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,639
A person without shame

47
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:24,319
deserves to be punished.

48
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,599
You were faking sleep.

49
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,479
Mother...

50
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,719
Nian...

51
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:33,120
Remember this.

52
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,639
In this world,

53
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:37,319
- paths are never paved for the weak.
- Mother.

54
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,879
You must strive to
grow to the highest point.

55
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,280
Mother.

56
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,240
The time has come.

57
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,400
Drown her.

58
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:54,639
Let's leave a mark.

59
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:57,000
In the next life,

60
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:59,080
you will be my child.

61
00:04:13,540 --> 00:04:17,420
(Fengqi Palace)

62
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,279
I

63
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,720
pay my respects to the Empress.

64
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,920
Long live the Empress.

65
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:32,120
Rise.

66
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,680
Thank you, Your Highness.

67
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,800
Be seated.

68
00:04:41,639 --> 00:04:43,920
I wonder why Your Majesty summoned me

69
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,120
and what your instructions are.

70
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,480
Senior Attendant Rou
committed no great fault.

71
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:50,360
You are her sister.

72
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:53,000
Why don't you plead for mercy
from the Dowager Consort?

73
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:57,160
Please listen, Your Highness.

74
00:04:57,439 --> 00:04:58,560
The Immortal Peach Tree

75
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,199
is the immortal tree of Mount Nanhua.

76
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,920
It withered due to my sister.

77
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,879
I was terrified in my heart.

78
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,319
I dared not plead for mercy.

79
00:05:06,879 --> 00:05:09,160
I only hope the heavens' anger
will soon be appeased

80
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:11,319
to protect the fate of Daliang.

81
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,720
Alright.

82
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,839
You may leave.

83
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,079
Thank you, Your Highness.

84
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:27,959
It seems the relationship
between these two sisters

85
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,240
is really not harmonious.

86
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,480
Has His Majesty

87
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,600
visited the Cold Palace?

88
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:36,839
He has not.

89
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:41,800
It seems His Majesty's
favor was only fleeting.

90
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,079
Poor Shen Zhinian, so young,

91
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,500
yet she's already in the Cold Palace.

92
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,800
A face as lovely as a flower,

93
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:50,279
yet it cannot
withstand the ravaging wind.

94
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,720
Before sunset today,

95
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:55,120
finish washing all these clothes.

96
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:55,879
Doing laundry?

97
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:57,690
Isn't that
the Palace Laundry Service's job?

98
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,780
Senior Attendant Liu said

99
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,600
Shen Zhinian must wash them herself.

100
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,000
No one is allowed to help her.

101
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,120
We have never even offended Liu Ruyan.

102
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,060
Why does she keep framing us
over and over again?

103
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:10,690
Now that we are in the Cold Palace,
she still bullies us like this.

104
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:13,040
Getting angry will only hurt yourself.

105
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,319
We'll find a way

106
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,319
to make them stop bringing clothes here.

107
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,600
Handan,

108
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:19,279
go chop some withered branches,

109
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,879
then bring me the itch-grass
we picked the other day.

110
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:24,910
You're so clever, Young Lady.

111
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,879
I'll go right now.

112
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,720
Young Lady,

113
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,639
after Liu Ruyan received
the clothes you washed,

114
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,950
she threw them into the fire pit.

115
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,759
The flames flared up,

116
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,250
and the whole room was filled
with ash mixed with itch-grass.

117
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:58,120
Now, her body and face
are covered in rashes.

118
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,720
These rashes won't fade

119
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,759
for at least ten days.

120
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,279
During this time,

121
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,800
she won't come to pester us.

122
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,519
You are brilliant, Young Lady.

123
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,879
But I still feel it's unfair for you.

124
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,759
Everything was going so smoothly,

125
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,720
and now,

126
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,000
we ended up in this dump.

127
00:07:15,759 --> 00:07:16,639
Look at this place.

128
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:19,260
Doesn't it look like our old courtyard
back at the Shen residence?

129
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:21,040
I think it's better than that.

130
00:07:21,050 --> 00:07:23,510
At least Madam Shen isn't here
to look for trouble every day.

131
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,270
You're so optimistic, Young Lady.

132
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,279
It's late.

133
00:07:26,290 --> 00:07:27,200
Let's get some sleep.

134
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,199
What should we do?

135
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:33,560
The wind has been so strong lately.

136
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,879
The window is completely broken.

137
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,839
What if a wild cat gets in tonight

138
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,319
and hurts you, Young Lady?

139
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:40,319
I'm only worried
that the "wild cat" won't come.

140
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,879
Handan,

141
00:07:42,439 --> 00:07:44,120
go take the itch-grass
we gathered today,

142
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,839
chop it up,

143
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,240
and scatter it on the window.

144
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,240
Yes.

145
00:07:58,439 --> 00:08:00,079
Seven days have already passed.

146
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,600
He actually hasn't come.

147
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,279
It seems

148
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,480
this time will be difficult.

149
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,160
Young Lady,

150
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:08,319
what should we do?

151
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,480
I need to send two letters out.

152
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:14,560
Who are they for, Young Lady?

153
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:17,040
One

154
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,319
is for Lu Jianglin.

155
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,519
And the other?

156
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,959
For Jiang Chen.

157
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:24,959
You're amazing, Young Lady.

158
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,399
I hope they'll be useful.

159
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:33,080
Your Majesty, these are the letters
Shen Zhinian sent out recently.

160
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:36,620
(To Lu Jianglin: Life is hard,
and my rice is almost gone)

161
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:41,380
(To Lord Jiang: Grant me ten sheets of
hemp paper and a stick of pine soot ink)

162
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,080
Asking one for rice

163
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,480
and the other for paper.

164
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,639
Her life in the Cold Palace

165
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,159
is lively indeed.

166
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,799
I thought you were quite at ease,

167
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,600
playing both sides.

168
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,600
Why the long face then?

169
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,990
Shen Nanqiao and Lu Jianglin
didn't leave the palace tonight.

170
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,639
They're staying with
Dowager Consort Liu.

171
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:55,919
So let them.

172
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,159
Why are you coughing?

173
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:59,399
Your Majesty asked me
to report the situation.

174
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,840
Go on.

175
00:10:01,850 --> 00:10:03,560
According to
the Dowager Consort's staff,

176
00:10:03,570 --> 00:10:05,890
Shen Nanqiao spent the whole way
badmouthing Shen Zhinian,

177
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:07,300
praising her with faint damnation.

178
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,320
The Dowager Consort now

179
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,519
utterly detests Shen Zhinian.

180
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:15,519
Did Lu Jianglin not
say a single word for her?

181
00:10:16,799 --> 00:10:17,840
Not a single word.

182
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,000
Useless trash.

183
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:31,200
(Cold Palace)

184
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:31,919
Strange.

185
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:33,960
Why did Shen Zhinian
write to you, Young Master?

186
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,919
Talking about orchids and magnolias,

187
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,519
it's all completely trivial.

188
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,960
The answer is already before us.

189
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,360
What is it?

190
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:50,120
To lure His Majesty here.

191
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:53,759
Do you mean that His Majesty
has truly fallen for her?

192
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:54,840
Whether it's true or false,

193
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,679
we'll know once we go in and see.

194
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:06,790
Be careful, Young Master.

195
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,200
Who's there?

196
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:23,520
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

197
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:30,480
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

198
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,480
♪If we don't meet♪

199
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:37,920
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

200
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:44,640
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

201
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:51,440
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

202
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:58,120
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

203
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:05,320
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

204
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:12,200
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

205
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:18,320
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

206
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:25,840
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

207
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:32,680
♪Wanting to fold
my heart into a paper kite♪

208
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:39,400
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

